Microsatellites located into the deletion were analyzed by PCR and capillary electrophoresis sizing of the products. Microsatellites were amplified using the following primers:
L17941, Forward: 5′- 6FAM-CTGGGTACTCTTCTGTGACA-3′;
Reverse: 5′-CTCTCTCCCCAACATGGTG-3′.
L29692, Forward: 5′-6FAM-TGTGTGTCTTCTGGGGGAGT-3′;
Reverse: 5′-CACAGCTAGCCACAGGCAG-3′
